      "widgets_values": [
        "### Hybrid workflow\n- `ByteDanceCreateImageAsset` handles the official ComfyUI real-human verification flow\n- `Seedance2` handles video generation through your custom node pack\n- Save both `asset_id` and `group_id`\n- If you are verifying for the first time, run the asset node first and complete the official link flow before expecting generation to work\n\n### Requirements\n- Updated ComfyUI with the built-in ByteDance nodes available\n- Logged into ComfyUI API nodes / partner access\n- `SeedanceApiKey` configured for `anyfast` if you want generation through this repo"
